Executive Profile
Robert O. Bond  President and Chief Operating Officer, Panhandle Eastern Pipe Line Co LP.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 4 different industries.57--
Background

		Mr. Robert O. Bond, also known as Rob, served as President and Chief Operating Officer of Penntex Midstream GP LLC of PennTex Midstream Partners, LP from August 2014 to November 1, 2016. Mr. Bond Co-Founded PennTex Midstream Partners, LLC and served as its Chief Operating Officer until November 1, 2016. Mr. Bond served as President and Chief Operating Officer of Panhandle Eastern Pipe Line Co Lp and Panhandle Energy, interstate natural gas pipeline operations of Southern ... Union Co. since April 4, 2005. Mr. Bond served as Senior Vice President - Pipeline Operations of Southern Union Co. since September 2005. Mr. Bond served as Chief Executive Officer at Panhandle Eastern Pipe Line Co LP. He served as President and Chief Operating Officer of Crosscountry Energy, LLC since April 2005. He served as Senior Vice President and Chief Commercial Officer for Panhandle Energy since November 2004. Mr. Bond served as Senior Vice President of Marketing at Panhandle Eastern Pipe Line Co Lp. since July 8, 2003. Since joining Panhandle Energy in February 2000 as Executive Director of Commercial Optimization, he served as Vice President of Optimization, Vice President of Marketing and Senior Vice President of Marketing. Prior to joining Crosscountry Energy, LLC, he served as Director of business development for Sonat Marketing Company from 1998 to 2000. He served as Managing Director for El Paso Energy and Tenneco Energy from 1984 to 1998. He is a Member of the Southern Gas Association and the National Energy Services Association and is active in numerous industry and trade association marketing events and conferences. Mr. Bond earned a Bachelor of Science degree in Economics from Texas A&M University.Read Full Background




